hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: We need someone with experience rose pharmacy it park Well, you know: The Mets suffered a second consecutive divisional collapse a few months later, Shea closed and Citi opened, Wright managed just 10 home runs the following year and felt his skull dented by a Matt Cain beanball, the team started losing like crazy, a GM and manager lost their jobs in 2010, scouts thought Wright was in decline, Wright recovered his All-Star form but the team remained bad, the Mets made Wright a very rich man and the fourth team captain in franchise history, he got engaged.
